Fix #103

The bug was caused by a too broad default seach scope for locating layouts.
It resulted in finding several files (e.g. for 'title_bar.xml').
The plugin then had a difficulty selecting the best file.

Added logging for better production diagnostics.

Add support for Unbinder (#97)

Adding support fo Unbinder which was added in ButterKnife 8.
Updated test-app to better reflect versions of current development tools.

* Added checkbox at the beginning of EntryHeader
* Added 'de-select all' checkbox behaviour
* Added a new View in test-app to test new behaviour

Add support for ButterKnife 8.0.0 #93

Unbinder is not-yet-supported.
Code for unbinding is not generated in Fragment's onDestroyView()
for ButterKnife 8.0.0.
